  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Cohollo</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Paolo_Puggioni_Colhollo_close_up.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Paolo Puggioni Colhollo close up.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/de/Paolo_Puggioni_Colhollo_close_up.jpg/350px-Paolo_Puggioni_Colhollo_close_up.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/de/Paolo_Puggioni_Colhollo_close_up.jpg/525px-Paolo_Puggioni_Colhollo_close_up.jpg 1.5x, /images/d/de/Paolo_Puggioni_Colhollo_close_up.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Colhollo, by Paolo Puggioni © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bloodrider\" title=\"Bloodrider\">Bloodrider</a> of Khal Drogo</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">Khal</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n~ <a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nUnidentified</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_1\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Cohollo</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodrider\" title=\"Bloodrider\">bloodrider</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">Khal</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cohollo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Cohollo\" title=\"Category:Images of Cohollo\">Images of Cohollo</a></div>\n<p>Cohollo is the oldest of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s bloodriders, a squat bald man with a crooked nose and a mouth full of broken teeth.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cohollo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Cohollo saved Drogo from <a href=\"/index.php/Sellswords\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellswords\">sellswords</a> when he was still young.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cohollo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cohollo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>As a wedding gift to the newly-wed <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> and Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>, Cohollo gives them an <i><a href=\"/index.php/Arakh\" title=\"Arakh\">arakh</a></i> chased in <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> bares steel during a feast in <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a> and threatens Daenerys, Drogo orders his bloodriders to seize him. <a href=\"/index.php/Qotho\" title=\"Qotho\">Qotho</a> pins Viserys while the others disarm him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Cohollo treats Daenerys kindly until she attempts to heal Drogo with the help of <a href=\"/index.php/Mirri_Maz_Duur\" title=\"Mirri Maz Duur\">Mirri Maz Duur</a>. Fearing the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Maegi\" title=\"Maegi\">maegi</a></i>, Cohollo and the other bloodriders attempt to stop her. Cohollo nearly slashes the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khaleesi\" title=\"Khaleesi\">khaleesi</a>'s</i> throat during the attempt, but he is killed by an arrow from <a href=\"/index.php/Aggo\" title=\"Aggo\">Aggo</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cohollo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gameofthrones.fandom.com/wiki/Cohollo\">Cohollo</a> on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gameofthrones.fandom.com\">Game of Thrones Wiki</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cohollo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 11\">Chapter 11</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_64\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 64\">Chapter 64</a>, Daenerys VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122437\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time u